 "title": "Meet Rainer",
 "summary": "On a bench in Organa Park on Ord Mantell, the medic Myiari chats with the newcomer spacer Rainier about the altercations she has gotten caught up in around the city. They are joined by Senator Tokoga, taking a break from his government sessions, and Myiari introduces the two men. Rainier, faintly suspicious of a senator who travels without guards, trades wary small talk before excusing himself to visit the Caamasi Gardens. Myiari and Tokoga linger to banter about her social life and her slow progress toward becoming a full doctor before parting ways to return to their respective duties.",
